# 📊 Business Intelligence Dashboard Suite | Power BI

> **A professional Business Intelligence Dashboard Suite built using Microsoft Power BI to transform raw business data into actionable insights through interactive dashboards, KPI tracking, and advanced analytics.**

---

## 🚀 Project Overview

This project showcases a complete **Business Intelligence Dashboard Suite** developed using the **Superstore Sales Dataset**. The dashboards are designed to help organizations monitor business performance, identify trends, evaluate KPIs, and support strategic decision-making through interactive visualizations.

The project consists of **five interconnected dashboards**, each focusing on a specific business domain.

---

## 📊 Dashboards Included

| Dashboard | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| 📌 Executive Dashboard | High-level overview of business performance with key KPIs and trends. |
| 📈 Sales Analysis Dashboard | Analyze sales trends, regional performance, and category-wise sales. |
| 📦 Product Performance Dashboard | Evaluate product sales, profitability, and best-performing products. |
| 👥 Customer Analysis Dashboard | Understand customer behavior, lifetime value, and customer segmentation. |
| 💰 Financial Analysis Dashboard | Monitor revenue, profit, margins, and overall financial performance. |

---

# ✨ Key Features

- 📊 Interactive KPI Cards
- 📈 Sales & Profit Analysis
- 👥 Customer Analytics
- 📦 Product Performance Tracking
- 💰 Financial Performance Monitoring
- 🌍 Regional Sales Analysis
- 🎯 Business KPI Reporting
- 🔍 Dynamic Filters & Slicers
- 📅 Time-based Trend Analysis
- 📉 Profitability Analysis
- 📌 Executive Business Overview
- ⚡ Interactive Visualizations

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Microsoft Power BI
- Power Query
- DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)
- Data Modeling
- CSV Dataset (Superstore)

